album.title: Hip Hop Moshpit by STOKED - Rage Mix

wiki.summary: “KNIGHT CRAWLER” sees Trippie Redd and the late Juice WRLD reuniting for a fast-paced track, in which the duo rap about popping pills, women, etc. The title of the track is most likely in reference to the 2014 film Nightcrawler. However, it could also be a reference to the Knightcrawler—a vehicle used by Batman—due to the fact that the song references cars like the Dodge Demon. Notably, the original version of the track used to be a Juice solo. The second verse was removed and replaced with Trippie’s. Read more on Last.fm.
